data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home nestled on a spacious lot w/ full basement. This property offers immense potential and is awaiting your personal touch.
The main level features a cozy living room, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. The adjacent kitchen provides ample open space to customize. Expansive wraparound deck offers views of the large, fenced-in backyard. 
The full basement provides endless possibilities: recreation area, home office, or additional storage. With a little TLC, this area can be transformed into a valuable extension of your living space. This property offers convenience and tranquility, near parks, schools, shopping centers, and easy access to major highways for commuting. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. With  fantastic potential and desirable features, this property is just waiting for your personal touch to turn it into a true gem. Seller to sell AS-IS and to make no repairs!
